          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Dwarka school is the school where I studied for more than 5 years. The school might not be big as it's foundation is still shallow but is still exponentially growing around it's areas that it owns. new grounds and sports facilities such as Volleyball court, basketball court are already implemented. To me this school has been a second abode apart from home. As to why is that is because of the staff and students that gather there. Teachers are very kind and attentive towards you, they become friends when in need and also strict at the same time. The teachers here are very knowledgeable and they do their utmost to educate the students. Students tend to  interact a lot, as many activities are conducted in the school.",
